      <title>Leetcode268</title>
      <link href="/2025/07/30/Leetcode268/"/>
      <url>/2025/07/30/Leetcode268/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="題目資訊"><a href="#題目資訊" class="headerlink" title="題目資訊"></a>題目資訊</h2><ul><li>題號：LeetCode 268  </li><li>難度：#Easy</li></ul><h2 id="題目說明"><a href="#題目說明" class="headerlink" title="題目說明"></a>題目說明</h2><p>給定一個包含 <code>n</code> 個不同數字的陣列 <code>nums</code>，這些數字來自 <code>0</code> 到 <code>n</code>，找出陣列中缺少的那一個數字。</p><hr><h2 id="範例"><a href="#範例" class="headerlink" title="範例"></a>範例</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Input: nums = [<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">1</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># n = 3，理想情況下應包含 [0, 1, 2, 3]</span></span><br><span class="line">Output: <span class="number">2</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="🔍-解題思路"><a href="#🔍-解題思路" class="headerlink" title="🔍 解題思路"></a>🔍 解題思路</h2><ol><li>使用 <code>range(n+1)</code> 生成從 <code>0</code> 到 <code>n</code> 的所有數字。</li><li>對每個數字檢查是否存在於 <code>nums</code> 中，若不存在即為缺失的數字。<br>✅ 完整程式碼（原始解法）</li></ol><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">missingNumber</span>(<span class="params">self, nums</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    leng = <span class="built_in">len</span>(nums)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(leng + <span class="number">1</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> i <span class="keyword">not</span> <span class="keyword">in</span> nums:</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> i</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="📌-小結與優化"><a href="#📌-小結與優化" class="headerlink" title="📌 小結與優化"></a>📌 小結與優化</h2><h4 id="優點："><a href="#優點：" class="headerlink" title="優點："></a>優點：</h4><ul><li>記憶體使用率低（超過 80% 的解答）。</li></ul><h4 id="缺點："><a href="#缺點：" class="headerlink" title="缺點："></a>缺點：</h4><ul><li>執行時間較長（僅超過約 10% 的解答），因為 <code>if i not in nums</code> 是 O(n) 操作。</li></ul><h4 id="優化建議："><a href="#優化建議：" class="headerlink" title="優化建議："></a>優化建議：</h4><ul><li>將 <code>nums</code> 轉換為 <code>set</code>，可以將查找時間從 O(n) 降為 O(1)。</li><li>或使用數學總和公式、異或技巧達到 O(n) 時間與 O(1) 空間。<br>🚀 優化範例：使用 set 提升查找效率</li></ul><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">missingNumber</span>(<span class="params">self, nums</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    num_set = <span class="built_in">set</span>(nums)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="built_in">len</span>(nums) + <span class="number">1</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> i <span class="keyword">not</span> <span class="keyword">in</span> num_set:</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> i</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
